{"tid":1944362,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手想領養貓(求推介)","createTime":"2020-03-26T10:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T16:08:15.000Z","uid":348503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8bbfca4952738fcf4ed1a542b3cac18a56d79233","tid":1944362,"uid":348503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:28:54.000Z","msg":"聽人講Spca啲貓好搶手，好難先領養到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲可以推薦一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩機構容易啲領養到貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋聽講有好多貓義工都會撚人一大輪最後唔比領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩機構係唔會撚人又容易領養到貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求各位幫幫手比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a999aaa7b4fd9b06aa47bc5461f02835719618dc","tid":1944362,"uid":149563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:36:58.000Z","msg":"貓嘅話好似間間都難<br />\n始終貓義工大部分都閪閪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過聽聞領養成貓（1歳以上）會易少少<br />\n巴打可以試下領養啲兩三歲嘅貓"},{"pid":"1d327a6b917a98ea67183e22deddfe8689dfd9fc","tid":1944362,"uid":149563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.lap.org.hk/adoptcat.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lap.org.hk%2Fadoptcat.aspx&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=7469583b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.lap.org.hk/adoptcat.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw 可以問下呢間<br />\n要家訪"},{"pid":"bda1dfe2581a398d73baa909af717124f4bc586e","tid":1944362,"uid":348503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d327a6b917a98ea67183e22deddfe8689dfd9fc","tid":1944